	<header class="postHeader">
				<div class="postKicker">
			<span class="kicker"><a href="http://bits.blogs.nytimes.com/category/executives-and-management/?module=BlogCategory&version=Blog Post&action=Click&contentCollection=Technology&pgtype=Blogs&region=Header">Executives and Management</a></span>
